Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_tx_int_reg

AGL_GMX_TX_INT_REG = Interrupt Register

Notes: UNDFLW[0], XSCOL[0], XSDEF[0], LATE_COL[0], PTP_LOST[0] will be reset when MIX0_CTL[RESET] is set to 1. UNDFLW[1], XSCOL[1], XSDEF[1], LATE_COL[1], PTP_LOST[1] will be reset when MIX1_CTL[RESET] is set to 1. PKO_NXA will bee reset when both MIX0/1_CTL[RESET] are set to 1.
